  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the conditions in ghetto immediately in I think in that winter, in 1940, '41 were probably even worse than they were later because it was winter, because there was a huge amount of people squeezed into those-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that area of Warsaw where the ghetto was, that was a central part-- north-- central north part of Warsaw, which was already before the war Jewish quarter, a Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it Must have been a Jewish area for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was-- most of it was tightly built together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were those big apartment blocks of five stories, six stories, all clo-- all closely together all around those courtyards.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them, if you went to in Nalewki, which was the main street, one of the main streets, of the ghetto, some of them were-- there was not one courtyard, but there were two, three, four courtyards.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were maybe more than 1,000 people living in such one apartment block.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were not only living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were as well working there because quite a lot of population of, of, of ghetto were-- particularly those who lived in Warsaw already before the war-- were living from small-- for-- they were-- had small workshops.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the kind of-- that was-- generally, the large part of the Jewish population of Warsaw was poor, really poor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had-- they managed to survive quite well before the war by, by, by doing-- working very hard and very menial trades very often.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And lots of them were doing things like-- they were doing like probably-- well, no one does in-- or maybe not anymore-- in Hong Kong or something.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
